45
00:04:27,820 --> 00:04:33,539
different to you? Would you be more willing
to place a bet in one match than in another?

46
00:04:33,539 --> 00:04:38,229
Or would you regard an even-money bet on either
player as equally reasonable for all three

47
00:04:38,229 --> 00:04:42,919
matches? In the lectures to follow, we'll
find that there are interesting arguments

48
00:04:42,919 --> 00:04:48,289
